{"title_page": "Clinton Township, Macomb County, Michigan", "text_new": "<!-- Infobox begins -->\n{{Infobox settlement\n|name                     = Clinton Charter Township, Michigan\n|official_name            = Charter Township of Clinton\n|other_name               =\n|native_name              = <!-- for cities whose native name is not in English -->\n|nickname                 =\n|settlement_type          = [[Charter township]]\n|motto                    =\n|image_skyline            =\n|imagesize                =\n|image_caption            =\n|image_flag               =\n|flag_size                =\n|image_seal               =\n|seal_size                =\n|image_shield             =\n|shield_size              =\n|image_blank_emblem       =\n|blank_emblem_size        =\n<!--\n| pushpin_map = USA\n| pushpin_map_caption = Location in the United States\n|pushpin_map_caption    =\n|pushpin_mapsize        =\n-->\n|pushpin_map            =Michigan\n|pushpin_label_position =left<!-- the position of the pushpin label: left, right, top, bottom, none -->\n|pushpin_label          =Clinton Township\n|pushpin_map_caption    =Location within the state of Michigan\n|pushpin_mapsize        =\n|image_map                = Clinton_Charter_Township_(Macomb),_MI_location.png\n|mapsize                  = 250\n|map_caption              = Location within [[Macomb County, Michigan|Macomb County]] \n|subdivision_type         = [[List of sovereign states|Country]]\n|subdivision_type1        = [[U.S. state|State]]\n|subdivision_type2        = [[List of counties in Michigan|County]]\n|subdivision_name         = United States\n|subdivision_name1        = [[Michigan]]\n|subdivision_name2        = [[Macomb County, Michigan|Macomb]]\n|subdivision_type3        =\n|subdivision_name3        =\n|subdivision_type4        =\n|subdivision_name4        =\n|government_footnotes     =\n|government_type          =\n|leader_title             = Supervisor\n|leader_name              = Robert J. Cannon\n|leader_